1
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,560
Bulletproof glass.

2
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,800
Signal jammer.

3
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,079
I've got the stuff.

4
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,440
Can you stop the countdown now?

5
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,480
Yes, you got it.

6
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,360
But it seems you're trapped.

7
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,560
It doesn't count as a completed mission.

8
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,360
The video footage you sent me

9
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,360
didn't mention that

10
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,920
anyone breaking into his room

11
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,280
would trigger the security system.

12
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,600
That's your mistake,

13
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,600
not mine.

14
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,400
Wait a minute.

15
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,880
You can hack into his surveillance system,

16
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,040
so can you hack into his security system too?

17
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:04,840
His security system is independent.

18
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,160
It's not connected to the network,

19
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,400
so I can't hack it.

20
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,400
Sorry, there's nothing I can do.

21
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,330
You have to figure it out yourself.

22
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,200
I already have the stuff.

23
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,040
But I've run into a situation.

24
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,640
Can you give me a bit more time?

25
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,480
That's against the rules of the game.

26
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,240
We should respect the rules.

27
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,920
Isn't your goal to get that passport?

28
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,440
If I fail,

29
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,600
you won't get it either.

30
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,659
It doesn't matter.

31
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,120
If you fail, there will be someone else to do it.

32
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:58,480
I've already alerted them.

33
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,440
If I fail and you find someone else,

34
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,000
won't that take more time?

35
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,220
Does efficiency mean nothing to you?

36
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,520
Help me.

37
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,180
I'm begging you, okay?

38
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,320
Help me.

39
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,410
Half an hour.

40
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,360
Give me another half an hour.

41
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,480
I just need half an hour.

42
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,520
I can give you half an hour.

43
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,800
But you have to pay a price for it.

44
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,530
Can you accept that?

45
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,960
What price?

46
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,840
You'll naturally find out when the time comes.

47
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:39,200
Okay, I accept.

48
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:08,640
Brothers!

49
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,900
He's here! Come quick!

50
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,240
Go! Chase him!

51
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,960
Don't run!

52
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,200
Stop!

53
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,600
The elevator!

54
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:00,520
Stop!

55
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,880
Stop!

56
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,570
I didn't expect you to really come.

57
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,040
Hello, sir.

58
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,970
Did you call for an errand service?

59
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,680
Yes.

60
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,210
Help me deliver something.

61
00:10:59,280 --> 00:10:59,800
Hello.

62
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,260
Your package has arrived.

63
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,730
I thought you didn't smoke.

64
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,740
Prepared this for you.

65
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:02,080
You are late.

66
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,720
There was a slight accident.

67
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:14,280
Why do you have so many enemies?

68
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:17,440
I was just trying to help a friend,

69
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:20,160
but things didn't go so smoothly.

70
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:22,440
And I couldn't find any other helpers for the moment.

71
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,240
So?

72
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:36,240
I owed you before.

73
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:39,600
Now we're even.

74
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,400
Thank you.

75
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:54,400
You need to treat your wound.

76
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:58,040
Let me take you home first.

77
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,000
No need.

78
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,970
You've already helped me a lot.

79
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:12,760
Then I'll get going.

80
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:33,360
I can give you half an hour,

81
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:35,800
but you must pay the price for it.

82
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:37,440
Can you accept that?

83
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:40,080
Do you know who it was?

84
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:42,280
Boss,

85
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:43,880
his hat and mask were in the way.

86
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:45,740
We couldn't see his face clearly.

87
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,240
Brother Long,

88
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,080
when we were in the elevator,

89
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,600
I pulled off his mask.

90
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,440
The security cameras should have caught his face.

91
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,760
Then hurry up and check it.

92
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,440
Okay.

93
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:56,520
Let's go.

94
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:08,480
The passport is lost.

95
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,720
I've sent someone to look for it.

96
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:12,180
We should get it back soon.

97
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,520
Got it.

98
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,170
As long as it's handled.

99
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,360
Ning, they're here.

100
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,080
What are you good at?
